    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>Using vaccine data combined with electronic health records, we report that mRNA boosters provide greater protection than a two-dose regimen against SARS-CoV-2 infection and related hospitalizations. The benefit of a booster was more evident in the elderly and those with comorbidities. These results support the case for COVID-19 boosters.</jats:p>",
